entry.title: Great Britain Tourism Survey
entry.summary: The survey is a national consumer survey measuring the volume and value of overnight trips taken by residents of the Great Britain. It is jointly sponsored by the Welsh Government, VisitEngland and VisitScotland. Results of the survey are published annually in the GB Tourist, with quarterly updates at a Wales level.Source agency: Welsh GovernmentDesignation: Official Statistics not designated as National StatisticsLanguage: EnglishAlternative title: Great Britain Tourism Survey - Results for Wales
